    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "7a4bf8df-6953-4505-b638-0b6c55405c46",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "The Boy &amp; the Prey",
        "Location": "LOCATION_EDGY_FOX",
        "PublicId": "129961495567",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/edgy/mission_fox/scene_fox_contractcreation.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 3d225332-645d-4979-b5e5-5ac3996eedf8).Image",
        "Description": "A young hitman in training, struck by his escaping target , ran home to report the outcome and to get his injuries mended. &quot;Boy,&quot; said the lad&apos;s mentor as he tended his wounds, &quot;the next time you meet your prey, strike swiftly and ferociously, and it will be as still as the night.&quot;\r\rNow grown, the hitman never forgot his mentor&apos;s lesson  of &quot;whatever you do, do with all your might&quot; and soon  became a legend of his trade.",
